data.title: May 13 Issue 2011
data.meta_description: May 13 Issue 2011 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Six seniors at James Hubert Blake High School reflect on memorable teachers who have influenced them. The annual Arts and Humanities Festival was held, featuring dance, orchestra, and art performances and galleries by students. Senior Katie Lingan participated in dance and photography, inspired by the talent of her peers. As graduation nears, seniors are preparing for prom and graduation ceremonies while dealing with mixed emotions about concluding their high school careers.
